---
title: Lemon Honey Chicken with baby potatoes and carrots
description: If you're craving a succulent chicken dish then you won't find one much better than this lemony honey chicken. The sweet and zesty sauce shines, while the tender cooked potatoes and veg provide the perfect pairing.
